associated_reports.name: Responses Needed
associated_reports.description: Shows records requiring response from the PI.
associated_reports.sql:
SELECT 
dt.id,
dt.select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
dt.return_call_availability_notes,
dt.questions_from_call_notes,
dt.results_link,
dt.select_result,
dt.pi_return_call_notes,
dt.master_id

FROM (
 SELECT id,
   master_id, bhs_assignment_id, created_at, select_result,
   select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
   return_call_availability_notes,
   questions_from_call_notes,
   results_link,
   pi_return_call_notes,
   rank()
 OVER (
  PARTITION BY master_id 
  ORDER BY created_at DESC
 ) AS r
 FROM activity_log_bhs_assignments

) AS dt

inner join player_infos pi on dt.master_id = pi.master_id

WHERE
  r = 1
AND
(  dt.select_result IS NULL or dt.select_result <> 'complete' )


ORDER BY
  dt.id DESC
;

associated_reports.name: Contact from PI
associated_reports.description: Shows contact messages from the PI that require an RA to respond.
associated_reports.sql:
SELECT 
dt.id,
dt.select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
dt.return_call_availability_notes,
dt.questions_from_call_notes,
dt.results_link,
dt.select_result,
dt.pi_return_call_notes,
dt.master_id

FROM (
 SELECT id,
   master_id, bhs_assignment_id, created_at, select_result,
   select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
   return_call_availability_notes,
   questions_from_call_notes,
   results_link,
   pi_return_call_notes, extra_log_type,
   rank()
 OVER (
  PARTITION BY master_id 
  ORDER BY created_at DESC
 ) AS r
 FROM activity_log_bhs_assignments
 WHERE extra_log_type IN ('respond_to_pi', 'contact_initiator')
) AS dt

inner join player_infos pi on dt.master_id = pi.master_id
WHERE
  r >= 1 AND dt.extra_log_type = 'contact_initiator'
AND
  r = 1 AND dt.extra_log_type <> 'respond_to_pi'

ORDER BY
  dt.created_at DESC
;

associated_reports.name: BHS Subjects Pending Sync
associated_reports.description: Show BHS subjects that have been created here, but have not yet been transferred from Zeus.
associated_reports.sql:
select b.master_id from bhs_assignments b
left join player_infos pi
on b.master_id = pi.master_id
where pi.id is null
;

associated_reports.name: Search BHS Player
associated_reports.description:
Search players by name, phone, email or ID.
Leave the search field empty to see all subjects.
associated_reports.sql:
select distinct m.id master_id, b.bhs_id,
pi.first_name, pi.middle_name, pi.last_name, pi.nick_name,
a.street, a.street2, a.city, a.state, a.zip, 
pc.data, pc.rec_type
from masters m
left join player_infos pi
on pi.master_id = m.id 
inner join bhs_assignments b
on m.id = b.master_id
left join addresses a
on m.id = a.master_id
left join player_contacts pc
on pc.master_id = m.id
where 
(
  :name is null 
  or pi.first_name ~* :name
  or pi.last_name ~* :name
  or pi.middle_name ~* :name
  or pi.nick_name ~* :name
  or( 
    pi.first_name ~* coalesce(split_part(:name, ' ', 1),'none')
    AND pi.last_name ~* coalesce(split_part(:name, ' ', 2),'none')
  )
) 
OR
(
  regexp_replace(pc.data, '\W+', '', 'g') ~* regexp_replace(:name, '\W+', '', 'g')
) 
OR
(
  :name is not null and
  b.bhs_id::varchar  = regexp_replace(:name, '[^0-9]*', '', 'g')
)
associated_reports.search_attrs:
name: 
  text: 
    all: true
    multiple: single

associated_reports.name: Responses Completed
associated_reports.description: Shows records with completed response from the PI.
associated_reports.sql:
SELECT 
dt.id,
dt.select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
dt.return_call_availability_notes,
dt.questions_from_call_notes,
dt.results_link,
dt.select_result,
dt.pi_return_call_notes,
dt.master_id

FROM (
 SELECT id,
   master_id, bhs_assignment_id, created_at, select_result,
   select_record_from_player_contact_phones ,
   return_call_availability_notes,
   questions_from_call_notes,
   results_link,
   pi_return_call_notes,
   rank()
 OVER (
  PARTITION BY master_id 
  ORDER BY created_at DESC
 ) AS r
 FROM activity_log_bhs_assignments

) AS dt
WHERE
  r = 1
AND
( dt.select_result = 'complete' )


ORDER BY
  created_at DESC
;
